  <h2>About WCAG</h2>
  <p>Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) is the international standard for making web content more accessible to people with disabilities. The <abbr title="Web Content Accessibility Guidelines">WCAG</abbr> requirements are called "success criteria" (SC).</p>
  <p>Learn more from the <a href="/WAI/intro/wcag.php">WCAG Overview</a>.</p>
